    "body": "I'll leave this one here for now :)\r\n\r\nThis should be done in https://github.com/sigp/signature-schemes/blob/master/src/keys.rs\r\n\r\nWe have two options:\r\na) Have `SecretKey::from_bytes()` include `modulus curve order` before returning the secret key. \r\nb) Having a check to ensure `0 <= secret_key < curve order` and returning Err() if not\r\n\r\nI'm leaning more towards b) as it's bad practice to have secret keys outside a curve order and modulate them in.\r\n",
